<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.11">
<l>nāḷkaḷōr nālaintu tiṅka ḷaḷavilē</l>
<l>tāḷai nimirttuc cakaṭattaic cāṭippōy</l>
<l>vāḷkoḷ vaḷaiyeyiṟ ṟāruyir vavviṉāṉ</l>
<l>tōḷka ḷiruntavā kāṇīrē curikuḻa līrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with spiraled curly hair, see the quality of the shoulders of he who,</l>
<l>at [only] four or five months, went and destroyed the cart</l>
<l>by stretching out [his] leg [and] snatched away the precious life</l>
<l>of [her with] bright, crooked teeth. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
